{"tid":2058102,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實大家點解要呃自己話M記係窮撚恩物?","createTime":"2020-06-10T02:10:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T03:10:52.000Z","uid":120123,"like":10,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d0c5dbedc1a1be488dc053855fb5230233083eda","tid":2058102,"uid":120123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T02:10:58.000Z","msg":"其實大大方方認左佢...<br />\nM記的確好食有咩問題....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n講真，你廿幾蚊，真係可以買幾個包食飽佢。但係一定唔好食。<br />\n但係M記真係，廿幾蚊買個餐，其實平心而論一定好食過你就咁食包....<br />\n<br />\n其實人地真係好食，同佢係藍冇關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n真係要罷食，我覺得要首先認清事實。係，人地係真係好食，性價比高。但係我地要用自己意志力戰勝佢。<br />\n真係冇錢，真係控制住自己，寧願食d冇咁好食的野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n假如認知錯誤。咁永遠有借口去原諒自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5f0e4cac59b877d5612ba487123bf77dcb299b0","tid":2058102,"uid":77643,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T02:13:19.000Z","msg":"樓主快走<br />\n我幫你頂住先"},{"pid":"7c396c0ca5f60863025b4944f938ee4f895c81dc","tid":2058102,"uid":128081,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T02:15:20.000Z","msg":"垃圾食物不了。啲包又乾又硬，薯條時鹹時淡。狗也不屌。"},{"pid":"714285b1d69888ac0ceda85aff8204d5c1777e23","tid":2058102,"uid":75372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T02:16:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"896333299801da12ff52d9848079b9918f4740d2","tid":2058102,"uid":32675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T02:17:06.000Z","msg":"金共門都好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1ca6b31b0f592f725bfcc13a97f5cd010b60724","tid":2058102,"uid":191453,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T02:18:02.000Z","msg":"比藉口自己去食M記的人好多都唔係食最平d餐的<img s